      Sportcasts: Game Notification
    %p
      Please verify your email by clicking the following link:
    %a{:href => "#{@verification_url}"} #{@verification_url}
    %div
      #{@away_team.name.titleize} @ #{home_team.name.titleize}
      #{@game.date.in_time_zone("Eastern Time (US & Canada)").strftime("%-l:%M%P")} ET
